Môn: Tiếng anh
SMART WORLD 6 - REVISION FOR THE FIRST SEMESTER TEST

I. PRONUNCIATION (Phát âm)

Choose the word whose underlined part is pronounced differently from that of the others.

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. puppets
B. shows
C. orders
D. stands
Đáp án: A (âm /s/, các từ còn lại âm /z/)

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. fixes
B. pushes
C. misses
D. goes
Đáp án: D (âm /z/, các từ còn lại âm /ɪz/)

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. fireworks
B. flowers
C. gifts
D. shops
Đáp án: B (âm /z/, các từ còn lại âm /s/ - Lưu ý: "gifts" /s/, "shops" /s/, "fireworks" /s/, "flowers" /z/. Đề bài có thể in lỗi hoặc đáp án là B)

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. history
B. biology
C. village
D. literature
Đáp án: B (âm /aɪ/, các từ còn lại âm /ɪ/)

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. indoor
B. festival
C. like
D. dinner
Đáp án: C (âm /aɪ/, các từ còn lại âm /ɪ/)

Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. light
B. stripe
C. slim
D. fine
Đáp án: C (âm /ɪ/, các từ còn lại âm /aɪ/)

Choose the word that has a different stress pattern from that of the others.

Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. secret
B. scary
C. event
D. outdoor
Đáp án: C (trọng âm 2, các từ còn lại trọng âm 1)

Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. balcony
B. subject
C. adventure
D. favorite
Đáp án: C (trọng âm 2, các từ còn lại trọng âm 1)

Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. selfish
B. picnic
C. hotel
D. homework
Đáp án: C (trọng âm 2, các từ còn lại trọng âm 1)

II. MULTIPLE CHOICE (Ngữ pháp & Từ vựng)

Choose the most suitable words or phrases to fill in the blanks.

We like English, physics ________ biology.
A. to
B. or
C. and
D. so
Đáp án: C

We love playing soccer ________ badminton in our free time.
A. and
B. or
C. on
D. with
Đáp án: A

There isn’t a gym ________ a swimming pool near my house.
A. and
B. or
C. but
D. for
Đáp án: B

She doesn’t like math ________ biology.
A. and
B. or
C. but
D. for
Đáp án: B

His hometown is in the south ________ Italy.
A. in
B. on
C. at
D. of
Đáp án: D

Cần Thơ is in the Mekong Delta, ________ the Hậu River.
A. for
B. in
C. on
D. at
Đáp án: C

The restaurant opens ________ Sundays.
A. of
B. for
C. at
D. on
Đáp án: D

Students don’t go to school ________ Sundays.
A. in
B. at
C. on
D. of
Đáp án: C

Tom has Biology, Geography ________ Friday.
A. at
B. on
C. in
D. with
Đáp án: B

Our Math lesson usually finishes ________ 4.00 p.m.
A. on
B. of
C. at
D. for
Đáp án: C

My brother sometimes plays game "Free Fire" with his friends ________ the evening.
A. on
B. for
C. at
D. in
Đáp án: D

What do you do ________ your free time?
A. on
B. in
C. at
D. to
Đáp án: B

My best friend is very kind ________ lazy.
A. but
B. and
C. so
D. or
Đáp án: A

Excuse me, what size are ________ pants over there?
A. this
B. that
C. these
D. those
Đáp án: D

The new ship has got a ________ with a lot of books.
A. cabin
B. library
C. swimming pool
D. shop
Đáp án: B

My friends and I ________ camping in the summer. We have a good time.
A. go usually
B. usually go
C. never go
D. go never
Đáp án: B

Nam ________ video games on Sundays.
A. often play
B. plays often
C. often plays
D. play often
Đáp án: C

Nam usually walks to school and he ________ late.
A. never is
B. never go
C. is never
D. are never
Đáp án: C

He has ________ and brown eyes.
A. short brown hair
B. brown short hair
C. a short brown hair
D. a brown short hair
Đáp án: A (Thứ tự tính từ: Kích thước - Màu sắc)

My sister has ________.
A. short black hair
B. short hair black
C. hair short hair
D. black short hair
Đáp án: A

She has ________.
A. long blond hair
B. blond long hair
C. hair long blond
D. long hair blond
Đáp án: A

My sister has ________ hair.
A. black long curly
B. long curly black
C. curly long black
D. long black curly
Đáp án: B (Thứ tự: Kích thước - Hình dáng - Màu sắc)

My favorite subject is math. What’s ________?
A. me
B. my
C. yours
D. her
Đáp án: C

What’s your favorite subject? ________ is physics.
A. I
B. My
C. Mine
D. Yours
Đáp án: C

My favorite sport is tennis. What is ________?
A. your
B. yours
C. my
D. mine
Đáp án: B

Do you have a ruler? ________ is at home.
A. Their
B. His
C. Ours
D. Mine
Đáp án: D

What’s Peter ________? -> He’s very kind and helpful.
A. do
B. doing
C. love
D. like
Đáp án: D (like trong câu hỏi tính cách)

Student A: "Where is your hometown?" -> Student B: "________"
A. I love my hometown.
B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.
C. My hometown is a big city.
D. My hometown is very good for growing rice.
Đáp án: B

My favorite sport is volleyball. What’s ________?
A. their
B. mine
C. yours
D. her
Đáp án: C

Anna: What does your best friend look like? -> Lucy: ________
A. She is slim and has long hair.
B. She is so friendly.
C. She likes going shopping.
D. She is eleven years old.
Đáp án: A

Can I borrow your eraser? I can’t find ________.
A. yours
B. me
C. my
D. mine
Đáp án: D

Student A: "What color eyes does your sister have?" – Student B: "________"
A. She has blue eyes.
B. She likes green.
C. She has brown hair.
D. She has fair skin.
Đáp án: A

Anna: "What does your best friend look like?" – Lucy: "________"
A. She is slim and has long hair.
B. She is so friendly.
C. She likes going shopping.
D. She is eleven years old.
Đáp án: A

Peter: "How often do you go swimming?" -> Jenny: "________"
A. I go swimming.
B. I sometimes go swimming.
C. I don’t like swimming.
D. I go swimming with my friends.
Đáp án: B

Student A: "Is he from Italy?" - Student B: "________"
A. No, he is
B. Yes, he is
C. Yes, he has.
D. No, he hasn’t.
Đáp án: B

Student A: "What kind of book is it?" – Student B: "________"
A. It’s a fantasy novel.
B. I like Harry Porter.
C. That’s a good idea.
D. Here you are.
Đáp án: A

David: "What are you doing tomorrow?" - Mai: "I’m ________ a barbecue at my house."
A. going
B. having
C. playing
D. making
Đáp án: B

Ben: "________ do people prepare for Christmas?" - Jim: "They decorate their homes."
A. Why
B. Who
C. How often
D. How
Đáp án: D

Student A: "Why don’t we have a picnic this weekend?" – Student B: "________"
A. Yes, we don’t
B. No, we do
C. Good idea
D. You’re welcome
Đáp án: C

Student A: "Why don’t you sign up for book club?" – Student B: "________"
A. Yes, good idea.
B. I was born in 2003.
C. I live in San Francisco.
D. I clean my bedroom.
Đáp án: A

Student A: "Where is your hometown?" – Student B: "________"
A. I love my hometown.
B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.
C. My hometown is a big city.
D. My hometown is very good for growing rice.
Đáp án: B

Student A: "Does your apartment have a gym?" - Student B: "________"
A. Yes, it is.
B. No, it isn’t.
C. Yes, it does.
D. No, it does.
Đáp án: C

III. SIGNS (Biển báo)

[Biển báo P - Parking]
A. You can’t park your car here.
B. You can park your car here.
C. There aren’t many cars here.
D. You can buy cars here.
Đáp án: B

[Biển báo STOP]
A. You must stop
B. You can’t stop
C. You can’t run
D. You can’t talk
Đáp án: A

[Biển báo cấm đỗ xe]
A. You can’t park your car here.
B. You can park your car here.
C. There aren’t many cars here.
D. You can buy cars here.
Đáp án: A

[Biển báo cấm ăn uống]
A. Smoking
B. No eating
C. No littering
D. No drinking
Đáp án: B (Biển thường bao gồm cả cấm ăn và uống, nhưng B là hợp lý nhất trong ngữ cảnh "No eating")

[Biển báo Open for Takeaway Only]
A. You can eat in this restaurant.
B. This restaurant doesn’t open.
C. You can’t buy food here.
D. You can’t eat inside restaurant.
Đáp án: D

[Biển báo Caution Wet Floor]
A. You can’t go
B. You must walk carefully
C. You can run faster
D. You will fall off
Đáp án: B

[Biển báo Slow Children at Play]
A. Children play here.
B. A park is nearby.
C. You shouldn’t go fast in this area.
D. Playing with the children is slow.
Đáp án: A (Hoặc C cũng đúng về nghĩa, nhưng A mô tả biển báo trực tiếp hơn)

[Biển báo Keep Off The Grass]
A. Don’t run in class.
B. Don’t step on grass.
C. No smoking
D. Take off your shoes
Đáp án: B

[Biển báo Please take off your shoes]
A. People don’t sell shoes in this place.
B. Please remove your shoes when you enter this place.
C. You can find shoes when you are in this place.
D. Don’t buy shoes when you enter this place.
Đáp án: B

[Biển báo 2m distance]
A. Come together.
B. Stand up in two lines.
C. Go in pairs.
D. Keep two meters away from people.
Đáp án: D

IV. VERB FORM (Chia động từ)

Chia động từ trong ngoặc:

Janet is very happy when she gets lucky money. (be)

Cần Thơ is a city in the south of Vietnam. (be)

The children are excited. (be)

I am twelve. (be)

She is happy because she gets good mark of the final test. (be)

My brother and I are students. (be)

There is a book on the desk. (be)

There is an airport in the city. (be)

There are many trees and flowers in my school garden. (be)

There are two chairs in the living room. (be)

There are a lot of pens on the table. (be)

He doesn't go to the library after school on Sundays. (not go)

She doesn't like sports. (not like)

The children don't go to school at weekends. (not go)

Lisa and Toby don't play soccer every day. (not play)

Peter doesn't have English on Fridays. (not have)

I like Math but she doesn't like Math. (not like)

Tom doesn't walk to school every day. (not walk)

What housework does your brother do? (do)

What time does she go to bed every night? (go)

Who do you live with? (live)

What housework does Jane do? (do)

What housework do they do? (do)

I am playing soccer with my friends now. (play)

He is listening to music in his room now. (listen)

She is making dinner with her mom now. (make)

Lan is watching TV with her father at present. (watch)

They are riding their bikes on the street at present. (ride)

Keep silent! You are talking so loudly. (talk)

We are doing our homework at present. (do)

Look! The baby is sleeping in the room. (sleep)

Look! My father is doing arts and crafts. (do)

Mark is having a party at home at the moment. (have)

The children are watching a movie at the moment. (watch)

Hurry up! We are waiting for you. (wait)

She is wearing yellow shoes at the moment. (wear)

Be careful! The car is going so fast. (go)

Keep silent! You are talking so loudly. (talk)

Toby doesn’t like reading books. (read)

Do you like playing table tennis? (play)

I really like learning English. (learn)

Toby loves singing. (sing)

I love using computers. (use)

He enjoys watering the plants. (water)

She enjoys playing video games after school. (play)

They often go swimming at the beach. (swim)

Nam’s family always goes running when they camp. (run)

Do you want to have a barbecue this Sunday? (have)

I want to make a birthday cake for my mother. (make)

Do you want to drink some coffee? (drink)

Tuấn would like to drink some tea. (drink)

He’d like to play badminton with his friend after school. (play)

Peter would like to watch TV after dinner. (watch)

You can give food or money. (give)

She can take part in the charity event. (take)

I can ride a bike. (ride)

Gorillas can climb tall trees. (climb)

People can visit the website if they need to donate. (visit)

V. MATCHING

Match the questions to the answers:

Table 1:

What does she look like? - D. She is tall and slim.

What’s she like? - A. She is funny.

Do you live in a house or an apartment? - B. We live in an apartment.

Does she have any brothers or sisters? - C. No, she doesn’t.

Table 2:

What is Mary like? - D. She is kind, active and sensitive.

How often does Laura play volleyball? - C. Sometimes.

Does your house have a big yard? - B. Yes, it does.

What are you doing this weekend? - A. I’m playing soccer with my brother.

Table 3:

How often do you go running? - D. I rarely go running.

What time does the bus leave? - A. It leaves at 9:30 am.

Who does the most housework in your family? - B. My dad does.

Do you usually go swimming on the weekends? - C. Yes, I do.

Table 4:

What time do you get up? - D. At 6:30.

What does she look like? - C. She is tall and slim.

What housework do you do? - B. I do the dishes.

How do the people prepare for Tet? - A. They decorate their houses.

Table 5:

How much are those shoes? - B. They are $10.

Which club do you want to sign up for? - A. I want to sign up for Soccer Club.

What’s your favorite book? - D. I like Harry Potter.

Is he wearing glasses? - C. Yes, he is.

VI. READING - TRUE/FALSE

Read the following passage. Decide if the statements are TRUE or FALSE:

Passage Context: "People have celebrated Tet in Vietnam for many years... Before Tet, people buy fruits and flowers..."

People buy fruits and flowers before Tet., Đúng

During Tet, children wear new clothes and don’t get lucky money., Sai (Trong bài: "wear new clothes and get lucky money")

Read the passages about Cần Thơ / Charlotte's Web (các đoạn văn ngắn ở ảnh 6) và đánh giá đúng sai:

Passage 2: Cần Thơ

Cần Thơ is in the north of Vietnam., Sai (Bài đọc: "in the south")

It is famous for its floating markets and beautiful rivers., Đúng

The weather is cool in Cần Thơ., Sai (Bài đọc: "The weather is hot")

Cần Thơ is an important center for business and transportation., Đúng

Passage 3: Charlotte's Web

Wilbur is a spider., Sai (Bài đọc: "A shy pig, Wilbur")

Mr. Zuckerman is kind., Sai (Bài đọc: "he is selfish")

Charlotte is a helpful spider., Đúng (Bài đọc: "She is a helpful friend")

Mr. Zuckerman thinks Wilbur is very funny., Sai (Bài đọc: "thinks Wilbur is writing them... Wilbur is amazing")

VII. CLOZE TEST (Điền từ vào đoạn văn)

Choose the word (A, B, C or D) that best fits the blank space:

Passage 1 (Her name is Hoa...):

...a small house near my house. She lives with her parents (1) _________ a small house...
Đáp án: A. in

She is tall (2) _________ thin.
Đáp án: C. and

She always (3) _________ glasses when she goes to school.
Đáp án: D. wears

She really likes (4) _________ comedy movies.
Đáp án: C. watching

In my class, she is (5) _________, she often makes her...
Đáp án: A. funny

...often makes her (6) _________ class love her so much.
Đáp án: A. friends

Passage 2 (Kim is a new friend...):

Kim is a new friend (1) _________ my class.
Đáp án: A. in

Kim is tall with long blond (2) _________ and blue eyes.
Đáp án: A. hair

...so she is (3) _________ a yellow T-shirt...
Đáp án: C. wearing

We are going (4) _________ at the mall...
Đáp án: A. shopping

...because she’s having a (5) _________ tonight.
Đáp án: B. party

...making pizza for the party (6) _________ watching TV.
Đáp án: D. and (hoặc C. but tùy ngữ cảnh, nhưng thường là 'and')

Passage 3 (My favorite book...):

My favorite book (1) _________ Yellow Flowers on the Green Grass.
Đáp án: B. is

The (2) _________ of the book is Nguyễn Nhật Ánh.
Đáp án: C. author

It is about Thiều (3) _________ the people around him.
Đáp án: A. and

I like the book because it (4) _________ us many beautiful things...
Đáp án: C. shows

...beautiful things (5) _________ Thiều's village.
Đáp án: B. in

I really (6) _________ this book.
Đáp án: D. like

Passage 4 (In Vietnam, people...):

In Vietnam, people (1) _________ many different festivals each year.
Đáp án: A. celebrate

Vietnamese people have to prepare a lot (2) _________ this festival.
Đáp án: C. for

...people buy fruits and (3) _________ from the market...
Đáp án: B. flowers

This (4) _________ very important...
Đáp án: C. is

...children wear new clothes (5) _________ get lucky money.
Đáp án: A. and

Everyone is happy and (6) _________ about the New Year.
Đáp án: B. excited

VIII. REARRANGE (Sắp xếp câu)

Rearrange the sentences:

free / you / on / Are / Saturday / ?
Đáp án: Are you free on Saturday?

do / they / can / What activities / there / ?
Đáp án: What activities can they do there?

or boy / your / Is / friend / a girl / ?
Đáp án: Is your friend a boy or a girl? (Hoặc: Is your friend a girl or a boy?)

you / What / doing / are / on Friday / ?
Đáp án: What are you doing on Friday?

the library / do you / How / go to / often / ?
Đáp án: How often do you go to the library?

the music / What time / performance / start / does / ?
Đáp án: What time does the music performance start?

often / on the weekends / play badminton / I / with my dad /.
Đáp án: I often play badminton with my dad on the weekends.

always / My mother / the supermarket / goes to / after work /.
Đáp án: My mother always goes to the supermarket after work.

My sister / at the mall / does / on Sundays / the shopping /.
Đáp án: My sister does the shopping at the mall on Sundays.

do the housework / John / his mom / helps / after school /.
Đáp án: John helps his mom do the housework after school.

love / I / like football / outdoor activities / doing /.
Đáp án: I love doing outdoor activities like football.

does / your father / do / What / housework / ? /
Đáp án: What housework does your father do?

buy / at the bookstore / new books / My parents / usually /.
Đáp án: My parents usually buy new books at the bookstore.

IX. REWRITE (Viết lại câu)

Rewrite the following sentences:

There is a balcony in my apartment.
Đáp án: My apartment has a balcony.

There are two bedrooms in my house.
Đáp án: My house has two bedrooms.

There are forty classrooms in my school.
Đáp án: My school has forty classrooms.

There are many trees and flowers in my garden.
Đáp án: My garden has many trees and flowers.

I like History best.
Đáp án: My favorite subject is History.

I like Physics best.
Đáp án: My favorite subject is Physics.

He likes Biology best.
Đáp án: His favorite subject is Biology.

My sister has long black hair.
Đáp án: My sister's hair is long and black.

He has short hair.
Đáp án: His hair is short.

Her hair is long and blond.
Đáp án: She has long blond hair.

I have long blond hair.
Đáp án: My hair is long and blond.

She has long dark hair.
Đáp án: Her hair is long and dark.

He has short dark hair.
Đáp án: His hair is short and dark.

I like acting.
Đáp án: I am interested in acting. (Hoặc: I am into acting.)

Nam loves reading books.
Đáp án: Nam is keen on reading books. (Hoặc: Nam is interested in reading books.)

We like playing soccer.
Đáp án: We are fond of playing soccer.

James loves doing exercise.
Đáp án: James is interested in doing exercise.

Minh likes playing tennis with his father.
Đáp án: Minh is into playing tennis with his father.

Emma enjoys dancing.
Đáp án: Emma is keen on dancing.

We enjoy playing soccer.
Đáp án: We are into playing soccer.

John wants to go swimming on the weekend.
Đáp án: John would like to go swimming on the weekend.

We want to have a picnic this weekend.
Đáp án: We would like to have a picnic this weekend.

I want to travel to many famous places in the world.
Đáp án: I'd like to travel to many famous places in the world.

